    <Fragment slot="title">
      Connecting You To <span class="hidden xl:inline">South African Culture of </span>
      <span class="text-accent dark:text-white"> Extraordinary Music Experiences.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      <span class="hidden sm:inline">
        <span class="font-semibold">SouthStateSound  </span> is where a passion for artistic expression meets the use of cutting edge digital communication methods to + tell your story your way.</span
      >
      <span class="block mb-1 sm:hidden font-bold text-blue-600">We believe in the power of art expression </span>
      and are dedicated to helping you discover the unique stories behind South African music.
