  <!-- Features Widget *************** -->

  <Features
    id="features"
    tagline="Express Your Art"
    title="We Tell Your Story"
    subtitle="We bring the platform and resources to help you create an online presence and digital footprint to express your art to find your community."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Public Relations',
        description:
          'Through our experience in content creation, analytics and creative development in putting together a pipeline of a targeted online PR strategy, to co-ordinating different set of A&R compaigns and catelogs to end-to end full-suite support on pushing press releases.This brings what all-in all provides a reputation management for artists and Media Relations in South African Music where a communinity of audience can find more about your story.',
        icon: 'tabler:brand-tailwind',
      },
      {
        title: 'Artist Development',
        description:
          'Our roster of talent that is under our creative support to get this suite adminstration of their musical work and in-depth market positioning, A&R coodination and full-suite digital strategy.',
        icon: 'tabler:components',
      },
      {
        title: 'Public Curated Playlists',
        description:
          'Creating secure, efficient, and user-friendly websites that deliver exceptional experiences and lasting value.',
        icon: 'tabler:list-check',
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    tagline="Recent New Releases"
    title="Discover Our Collection"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Echoes Before The Verse',
        description:
          'AndyDeep & SemiLoopz Bring us the most anticipated debut project that begins a new music collection we are putting together for the next rollout of an Official Joint Ep. Stay Tuned!',
      },
      {
        title: 'Orbiting Shadows(Dropping Soon)',
        description:
          'SemiLoopz With AndyDeep on cooking an Exclusive unreleased project where the journey to the House of music to try bring the old Dub Mix sound of the soulful and deep house music the stems from in the South Africa space.',
      },

    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80',
      alt: 'Colorful Image',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Grow an online presence that truly represents you.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent">Editorial Insights</div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isAfterContent
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Streaming's Flat Fee: The Volume Game for Artist ROI',
        description: `In this new paradigm, music is essentially rented. Streaming services offer a vastdigital library and for artists or this means their work is priced equally across the board but a fraction of a penny per stream.This flat fee model or a radical departure from the per-unit sales of cassettes and CDs, means that volume plays a big part in the return on investment (ROI) of the intellectual property (IP).`,
      },
      {
        title: 'Music as Content: The Paradox of Cheap Production and Expensive Sales',
        description:
          'In 2025 music is increasingly packaged as content like any other media or increasing the demand for free or near-free access. This has ironically contributed to a scenario where the actual product itself is cheaper to make but more expensive to sell.This democratization of creation has indeed made the actual product far much cheaper to make.However the subsequent battle for attention and monetization in a saturated market makes it remarkably expensive to sell or generate meaningful revenue from recorded music.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Beyond Production: The Escalating Costs of Digital Music Promotion',
        description:
          "Today the core costs of manufacturing music and though slightly reduced due to the absence of physical production or have largely shifted.The aim is to get your music in front of people or rather than the other way around and as was often the case with established record labels and radio play in the past.",
      },

    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600132806370-bf17e65e942f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2194&q=80',
      alt: 'Blueprint Image',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">Welcome To Our Roster?</Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent">Creative A&R Partners</div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Content Widget **************** -->

  <Content
    isReversed
    isAfterContent
    items={[
      {
        title: 'AndyDeep(Artist/Producer)',
        description:
          'Andy has been writing music for a minute now since the 2015 while he was still working his recipe of his own sound in the Deep House genre which is what he started playing as Dj around the local resisdent.',
      },
      {
        title: 'SemiLoopz(Band/Studio)',
        description:
          'A music band and studio outlet from the city of Bloemfontein has been working with artists that part of southstatesound to help them mainly to recording artist demos and final audio recordings to the end product that both aligns with the common vision.',
      },

    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611462985358-60d3498e0364?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80',
      alt: 'Astronauts Image',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">Established to foster growth and progress.</Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Steps Widget ****************** -->

  <Steps
    title="Let Us Tell Your Story Your Way."
    items={[
      {
        title: '1. Solution: <span class="font-medium">Paid Blog Posts</span>',
        description:
          "Our main digital outlet for promoting new music is press releases to increase brand awareness using organic ads(Visuals) as blogs have become have become an incredibly easy and affordable way to reach an audience would have inaccessible beforehand. Provide services to not only provide our audience with information and gainn insights into the market.",
        icon: 'tabler:package',
      },
      {
        title: '2. Solution: <span class="font-medium">Talent Precurement</span>',
        description:
          "At Soutstatesound we believe our concentracted support and focus provide a benefi to independent artists who are looking for promotions and we can't afford the risk of an artist not generating revenue early on it's development stages. In exchange for a quater of the return for the services and promotional efforts as we as our ability to help build the the brand and audience/listerners.",
        icon: 'tabler:letter-case',
      },
      {
        title: '3. Solution: <span class="font-medium">Playlist Placement</span>',
        description:
          'Our budget will be split between two channels for Paid Posts and Public Playlists which determines ability to get placements on playlist that we believe align with our artists audience and target demographics across Spotify and Apple Music.',
        icon: 'tabler:paint',
      },
      {
        title: 'Release PR Rollout!',
        icon: 'tabler:check',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616198814651-e71f960c3180?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=987&q=80',
      alt: 'Steps image',
    }}
  />

  <!-- Features2 Widget ************** -->

  <Features2
    title="We Sell Music"
    subtitle="Our approach is digital-only strategy allows us to keep both fixed and variable costs relatively low and to keep expanses at a minimum in our first year of operations of each projects to instead free up capital for promotional efforts need to sell music."
    tagline="Solutions"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Press Release',
        description: "Our focus is towards helping Artists reach their proper target audience with our vast array of media outlets and industry standard blogs to insights into a more targeted promo coverage paid, owned or earned for your digital product or music.",
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:template',
      },
      {
        title: 'Publishing and Bookings Solutions',
        description:
          "We provide online support for co-ordinating your A&R to managing bookings where create market positioning and some creative solutions that are the bottleneck problems in your workflow as an artist/musician to a data-driven platform that extract insights over the internet to making strategic decisions to communicate to your target market.",
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:gallery',
      },
      {
        title: 'Public Curated Playlists',
        description:
          'We give back to same community of talented creatives and music listers that inspired us to start what we do since our inception as being to document South African Local Commercial music for consumers or listers that are looking for new and specific upcoming types of sounds. We want to make it an easy process for them to find and stream Mzansi's music, is based on our ability to look out and lock-in latest exclusive and recent released songs or records for placements on playlists owned or earned that we believe align or reflect types soound or Experience the audience and target demographic is currently listerning.',
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:approval',
      },

    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent">Word Of Mouth</div>
    </Fragment>
  </Features2>

  <!-- HighlightedPosts Widget ******* -->

  <BlogLatestPosts
    title="Cracking the Creative Code"
    information={`Let's move beyond generic connections and create promotion that stand out.
                        The vibrant pulse of South African music is constantly evolving, with exciting new artists and sounds bubbling up from every corner of Mzansi. Forget algorithms dictated by global trends; the real magic happens within our communities.In 2025 the spotlight is on the power of shared musical experiences through public curated playlists.
                `}
  />

  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Explore the connection between music and South African culture."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Why SouthStateSound?',
        description:
          "In today's saturated music market, talent alone isn't enough. Music promotion is essential to cut through the noise, get your music heard by the right audiences, and build a lasting career. It's about turning listeners into fans and fans into a dedicated community.",
      },
      {
        title: 'Why is PR important for musicians?',
        description:
          'PR is vital for building an artist's brand and reputation. We work to secure media coverage, craft your unique story, and build relationships with journalists, bloggers, and radio DJs. This adds credibility and helps control your public image, making you a more attractive prospect to the industry and fans.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Are there public collaborative playlists in South Africa?',
        description:
          "Yes, collaborative playlists exist on all major streaming platforms like Spotify and Apple Music. While many are private, there are public ones, and we can help artists get placed on them to increase their reach.",
      },
      {
        title: "What is the difference between Promotion and development for musicians?",
        description:
          "Promotion is focused on getting a finished product in front of an audience. It's the "push" phase. Development is a long-term strategy focused on building the artist as a brandâ€”refining their sound, image, songwriting, and live performance. We can work with you on both, ensuring your music is ready for promotion and your brand is ready for the world.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How much does music PR cost in South Africa?',
        description:
          "Music PR costs vary widely based on the artist's level and the scope of the campaign. For an emerging artist, a project-based campaign could range from a few thousand Rands to R15,000. Top-tier artists with more extensive needs can expect costs to be significantly higher. We work with each client to create a tailored plan that fits their budget and goals.",
      },

    ]}
  />

  <!-- Stats Widget ****************** -->

  <Stats
    stats={[
      { title: 'Established Since', amount: '2024' },
      { title: 'Artist & Repotoire', amount: '2' },
      { title: 'Collaborations', amount: '6' },
      { title: 'Sponsorships', amount: '2' },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- CallToAction Widget *********** -->

  <CallToAction
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Follow Us On Socials',
        href: 'https://www.instagram.com/southstatesound.space',
        target: '_blank',
        icon: 'tabler:download',
      },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      SouthStateSound&nbsp;+&nbsp;<br class="block sm:hidden" /><span class="sm:whitespace-nowrap">A Music Promotion Company</span>
